        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/hk-spellbreaker/">&lt;p&gt;This is a specialized build, intended for use in the final fight of Raid Wing 4 (Deimos). This build can be made comfortable and yet retains a high skill ceiling to allow the hand kiter to contribute to the team from far.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
