&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Food: &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;91805&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Cilantro Lime Sous-Vide Steak or &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;41569&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Bowl of Sweet and Spicy Butternut Squash Soup&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
